name: The AI Revolution: The Road to Superintelligence
description: Comprehensive guide to artificial intelligence development and its impact on society. Covers machine learning, neural networks, and future AI capabilities.

name: Clean Code: A Handbook of Agile Software Craftsmanship
description: Essential guide for software developers on writing clean, maintainable code. Covers best practices, refactoring techniques, and design patterns.

name: The Psychology of Money: Timeless Lessons on Wealth
description: Fascinating exploration of how people think about money and make financial decisions. Offers practical insights for better money management.

name: Dune: Frank Herbert's Epic Science Fiction Masterpiece
description: Classic science fiction novel set on the desert planet Arrakis. Epic story of politics, religion, and ecology in a distant future.

name: Atomic Habits: Tiny Changes, Remarkable Results
description: Practical guide to building good habits and breaking bad ones. Evidence-based strategies for personal and professional improvement.

name: The Lean Startup: How Today's Entrepreneurs Use Continuous Innovation
description: Revolutionary approach to business startups focusing on rapid iteration and customer feedback. Essential reading for entrepreneurs.

name: Sapiens: A Brief History of Humankind
description: Engaging exploration of human history from the Stone Age to the modern era. Challenges conventional understanding of human development.

name: Design Thinking: A Guide to Creative Problem Solving
description: Comprehensive introduction to design thinking methodology for innovation and problem-solving across various domains and industries.
